code: // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ public long getTimestampForRecord(T record, long kafkaEventTimestamp) {     return timestampsAndWatermarks.extractTimestamp(record, kafkaEventTimestamp). }

public long getCurrentWatermarkTimestamp() {     Watermark wm = timestampsAndWatermarks.getCurrentWatermark().     if (wm != null) {         partitionWatermark = Math.max(partitionWatermark, wm.getTimestamp()).     }     return partitionWatermark. }

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------ @Override public String toString() {     return "KafkaTopicPartitionStateWithPeriodicWatermarks: partition=" + getKafkaTopicPartition() + ", offset=" + getOffset() + ", watermark=" + partitionWatermark. }
